com.rift.coad.lib.httpd
Class CookieWrapper

java.lang.Object
  com.rift.coad.lib.httpd.CookieWrapper

public class CookieWrapper
extends java.lang.Object

This class is responsible for wrapping the access to the cookie information containied within, and for parsing cookie headers.
